        "collapsible_tab_Ta8cMT": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Made in Italy",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>Our marinière are crafted just a few kilometers from Venice, in a region renowned for its artisanal expertise and its role in producing garments for some of the world’s most famous high-fashion brands. Each piece is meticulously made from fine merino wool, celebrated for its natural softness and thermo-regulating properties. We work closely with a small, family-run workshop, fostering a partnership built on trust, craftsmanship, and a shared passion for quality.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_9wCejz": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Merino Wool from Italy",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>We have chosen one of the best manufacturers in the world of merino wool: <strong>Tollegno 1900</strong>. It is a historic Italian company specializing in the production of the highest quality wools. Located in the town of Tollegno, in the province of Biella, at the foot of the Piedmont Alps, Tollegno 1900 operates ethically and holds the most important eco-certifications in the textile industry, making it a <strong>green and sustainable company.</strong></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_T6nwD3": {
