          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p><strong>Shipping is free worldwide.</strong></p><p>Once your Marinière is dispatched, you'll receive an email with tracking details. We ship all over the world. And if you’re based in the EU, we will be sending your items directly from Italy so that you won’t incur additional customs fees.</p><p>If for any reason you wanted to return your Marinière, we accept returns within 14 days of delivery as long as the Marinièere is in perfect condition.</p>",
